des:
Alaska state is unofficially nicknamed "The Last Frontier", "The Land of the Midnight Sun", and the "Seward's Icebox". Alaska doesn't share a border with any US states, instead bordering with the Canadian states of Yukon and British Columbia.

Know more such interesting facts with this skill. 

Source: https://www.thefactsite.com/alaska-facts/
